{
  "stem": "13981.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- they must have come from Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, personally, do not know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But since Ilse Koch was camp commander there, they must have come from there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Yugoslavs came to us with their pictures for reproduction, of which you saw copies.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They needed reproduction when their case came up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the judges got the pictures, and the defense lawyers, and the prosecution so they would know what it was all about, and reproduce it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I said, when the Yugoslav delegation or delegate came in and asked me, can you make us so many copies, I said yes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How about could I have a copy?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, help yourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how I got the atrocities in my possession that the Yugoslavs had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So your responsibility was to bring it into the courtroom proceedings?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Proceedings.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We also presented films.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now I remember [LAUGHS] another funny thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a Russian film to show, and somehow I had put the reel backwards.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other-- it started at the end, or upside down or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyhow, it was wrong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And with me was one of the Russian guys that was-- and when-- when I showed him-- when the picture started, it started wrong.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had to reverse it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, he couldn't speak English, and I couldn't speak-- but he-- he did like this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If I would have done that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He said, it would have been my neck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] as I said, organizational charts.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember another thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Ohlendorf, I believe it was, a Nazi SS General who was responsible for millions of killings on the Eastern Front, I was seated from him like four or five feet.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
